snippet.textDisplay:
Fringilla Vigo is black........ You altered the story of Books already.
As she is Nilfgaardian, now there have to be black Nilfgaardians. Nilfgaardians are dipected as pale with dark hair. I don't understand why you have to "diversify" everything these days. The story is based of Slavic-Polish culture, if you made a film based off African culture I would be mad if you added Asians or white people to it.
Just stop with the politics. I am a huge fan of the Witcher books and video games. I have played Witcher, Witcher 2 Assassin's of Kings and Witcher 3 wild hunt over 20 times each. I have read the books like the last wish. I have even watched the Hexer (based of the books).
To see this truly makes me sad.

Edit: At 0:50, who is this person supposed to be? Can't be Vilgefortz.
